title: March, Stone Bridge area, Tiverton basin views.
description: Available March 1 as unfurnished with a year's lease.  Beautiful historic home built in 1869 conveniently located in The Stone Bridge Neighborhood proudly perched across the street from the Sakonnet River and the Tiverton Basin less than a mile from the highway, less 30 minutes from Downtown Newport, the War College, Bristol, Portsmouth, and Providence.  Features include fully applianced kitchen with dishwasher, laundry machines in unit not the basement, owner maintains landscaping, inviting front porch that features the west facing water views, full basement for storage.  Tenants pay for utilities: gas heat, electricity, and water.  Owner maintains lawn and landscaping. Pets are possible but there is a $100/month pet rent.  $2500 security deposit required.  Application is free but verification of income and a credit report required.  Please call for an appointment.

title: Island Park waterfront 2nd floor apt, rent incl heat plus wifi plus...
description: Available for  immediate occupancy as an unfurnished apartment with a year's lease.  Rent is $1,600 month but that includes what may be $300 month... gas heat, water, hot water, trash pickup, WIFI, and basic cable. Tenant would pay for electricity.  The pictures show updates are ongoing and this is a waterfront 2nd floor apartment with a large private deck that takes advantage of the fantastic water-views spanning peaceful Blue Bell Cove in Island Park.  This house has 2 apartment on the 2nd floor and Downstairs, on the 1st floor, is Morarty's Liguor Locker.  It is conveniently located less than 30 minutes from Downtown Newport and a few miles from Tiverton, Middletown, Bristol and Roger Williams University.  In the apartment there is a fully applianced eat in kitchen that looks out the sliding glass door to an oversized deck that has the views plus a dishwasher and over the stove microwave .  There are laundry machines in place along with carpeting in the living room and bedrooms.  There are also 2 off-street parking spaces.  Some pets may be possible with a $50 pet rent.  Security deposit equal to one month's rent is required.  Call for an appointment.

title: >>>HOUSE FOR RENT; 3 BEDROOMS; 2 FLOORS; 1 BATH
description: This house is near the water on Stafford Pond. It has 1600 sq ft living space. 3 bedrooms upstairs (2 are small). There's 1 full bath on the first floor. Full eat-in kitchen. 2 other rooms on first floor. Washer/dryer hook-up in one of the downstairs rooms with a louvered door.  No basement.
Propane heat, well water. No utilities are included.
It was completely gutted and rebuilt. Highest quality spray foam insulation in all exterior walls and roof.
The contractor is completing the installation of the heating system then the floors will be installed then the kitchen.
I don't expect it to be ready for viewing before March 2020.
The rent has yet to be set. The rent amount listed is approximate for now.
NO PETS. NO SMOKING. NO VAPING (or anything else that causes odors in the house).
